tent metaphor that keeps inspiring new interpretations.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aGroup identity. 0aSocial sciencesxPhilosophy. 4aGesellschaft. 4aKultursoziologie. 4aMenschenbild. 4aMetapher. 4aPhilosophiegeschichte. 4aSozialität. 4aSozialphilosophie. 4aSozialtheorie. 4aSoziologie. 4aSoziologische Theorie. 4aWeltanschauung. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh  aConcept of Man.  aHistory of Philosophy.  aMetaphor.  aSocial Philosophy.  aSocial Relations.  aSocial Theory.  aSociety.  aSociological Theory.  aSociology of Culture.  aSociology.  aWorldview.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Complete Package 2014z9783110369526oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2014z9783110370416oZDB-23-DSW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014z9783111025223oZDB-23-TGP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9783110489842oZDB-23-TGP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript: Complete eBook-Package 2014z9783110401226oZDB-23-TGP0 cprintz978383762727540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/transcript.9783839427279?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839427279423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839427279/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2014  aZDB-23-DSWb2014  aZDB-23-TGPb2014  aZDB-23-TGPc2014d2016